dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Portage County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature clss within the geodatabase, Portage_Roads_YE2016.gdb. Also included in this geodatabase is the right of way layer 'PORTAGE_ROW_YE2016'.[The Centerline data set is a vector representation of center of pavement in the County of Portage, Wisconsin. The centerlines are digitized from 1:12000 digital orthophotography or entered by coordinate geometry.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
